Class StreamEditor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sdklite.sed.StreamEditor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class StreamEditor
extends Object
implements Closeable
    Represents a stream editor, it could be used for binary file direct reading and writing without buffer
